sentence.text: Conversely, Th17 cells and their effector molecules interleukin 17A (IL-17A), IL-17F, interferon (adaptive immune response)γ, tumor necrosis factor (negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II)α, and granulocyte-macrophage colony-stimulating factor (positive regulation of cell proliferation) are implicated in the pathology of rheumatoid arthritis (RA).
